The penne vodka could be better than some italian restaurants.... They know what they are doing here.  The family that owns this place also owns brookside diner (which is also outstanding).  I would give this place your business before going ANYWHERE ELSE. Seriously never had better tasting food and service... like... at any diner.  And this place is cleaner than any diner I've ever seen.   Just phenomenal.  Flat out phenomenal.  If I could give more than 5 stars I would
